The paper discusses the challenges and opportunities of using Big Data in transportation systems, which involves issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), data management (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper emphasizes the importance of privacy in handling transportation data, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
